data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: There are two men rowing a boat. One boy is wearing a blue shirt while another boy is wearing a shirt in red and white. There is also a white yacht in the background and a person is standing on the top floor of the yacht. He might be the captain of that luxury yacht. The weather is cloudy, which implies that there might be a coming thunderstorm. This photo might be taken in the middle of an ocean.
